{"tid":1101850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"出價3千(台幣)槍殺教授！槍手竟不會開槍","createTime":"2019-04-11T10:03:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T05:16:56.000Z","uid":75969,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cc9e640b3688ec2f6ba82e3026d86d181d15206b","tid":1101850,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:03:14.000Z","msg":"記者於慶璇／桃園報導<br />\n<br />\n王姓男子2年前以3000元接受委託，前往桃園一所科大槍殺廖姓教師，但王嫌開槍前卻忘了「拉滑套」<span style=\"color: red;\">，2度擊發失敗，最後改持棍棒痛毆廖師後逃逸</span>，檢方依殺人未遂等罪嫌起訴他，但法院審理時卻改依傷害、非法持有子彈判他7個月，得易科罰金，另依加重竊盜判他7個月。<br />\n<br />\n檢警調查，王男2017年2月17日接受不明人士出價3000元槍殺廖姓教授，當日上午，王男事先跑到淡水一處社區地下室，竊取一輛自小客車車牌，改裝在自己車上，下午持槍潛入科大地下室停車，找到廖師的車子後，埋伏在附近。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ih9UJlHkjUoiQ0nwT0szCw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/073f46de0b6c16a37a5de23e75853bbe\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fih9UJlHkjUoiQ0nwT0szCw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F073f46de0b6c16a37a5de23e75853bbe&h=a292a6d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廖師與妻下午4時許現身停車場，王男趁著廖男打開後車廂放東西時，搖下車窗持槍瞄準，但王男卻忘了拉滑套，導致子彈未擊發，隨後又二度瞄準，子彈沒擊發直接掉落地面。廖男見狀後嚇得逃離，王男只好拿起車裡預藏棍棒追打，導致廖男左膝、小腿擦挫傷。<br />\n<br />\n王男犯案後駕車逃逸，並將槍管、竊來的車牌一併丟棄溪流，警方循線查獲王男，並在後車廂起獲鐵棍、子彈等，王男否認殺人犯意，辯稱自己只有開1槍，並且是朝廖男大腿擊發，但槍壞了才會拿鐵棍打他。<br />\n<br />\n檢方勘驗監視器，另發現王男手機裡有廖師照片及車號截圖，依殺人未遂、加重竊盜及槍砲等罪嫌起訴他，但法院審理後，卻改依非法持有子彈罪判刑3個月、傷害罪判刑5個月，2罪合併應執行7個月，得易科罰金；另依攜帶凶器侵入住宅竊盜罪判處7個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%87%BA%E5%83%B93%E5%8D%83%E6%A7%8D%E6%AE%BA%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88-%E6%A7%8D%E6%89%8B%E7%AB%9F%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D-061014811.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%2583%25B93%25E5%258D%2583%25E6%25A7%258D%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%258E%2588-%25E6%25A7%258D%25E6%2589%258B%25E7%25AB%259F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%25A7%258D-061014811.html&d=KS%2FaBsiOfKbE8rejl7UGUmWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=dd56328b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%87%BA%E5%83%B93%E5%8D%83%E6%A7%8D%E6%AE%BA%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88-%E6%A7%8D%E6%89%8B%E7%AB%9F%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D-061014811.html</a><br />\n<br />\n好平<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68aaa790d0d89cff06cda507dcadb7e0550ad79c","tid":1101850,"uid":125168,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:05:13.000Z","msg":"幾百蚊港紙請到乜嘢殺手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f12d81a495ba123f40236eb8e58703b8fe6f69e","tid":1101850,"uid":164920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:07:15.000Z","msg":"台仔唔係要服兵役架咩？掹雞都唔識？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4693dd8b56added126d8e49acb95c0a2127f9f8e","tid":1101850,"uid":244105,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3f12d81a495ba123f40236eb8e58703b8fe6f69e","tid":1101850,"uid":164920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:07:15.000Z","msg":"台仔唔係要服兵役架咩？掹雞都唔識？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:28:30.000Z","msg":"識既唔止收3000TWD啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e921162df37079a6f907a2d364ae3ea1cbb4163b","tid":1101850,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T01:11:25.000Z","msg":"文入面話要rack slide<br />\